OL,4,Cexpected in Parliament 'next month'
OL,6,FPost Office Kevin Hollinrake minister
OL,7,Fsaid he hopes all the convictions will
OL,8,Fbe "overturned by July" and that he
OL,9,F"very much hopes" compensation will be
OL,10,Fpaid before the next general election,
OL,11,Falthough he joked: "I can't tell when
OL,12,Fthe general election is going to be so
OL,13,FI can't specifically say yes to the
OL,14,Fquestion."
