OL,6,FHe was speaking as he updated MPs on
OL,7,Fthe Government's plans, also telling
OL,8,Fthe Commons that convictions would be
OL,9,Fquashed as soon as the proposals
OL,10,Fbecome law "without the need for
OL,11,Fpeople to apply to have their
OL,12,Fconvictions overturned".
OL,14,FMr Hollinrake's appearance in the
OL,15,FCommons comes after he announced
OL,16,Ffurther details of the planned
OL,17,Flegislation in a written statement to
OL,18,FMPs.
