OL,3,CLaw to exonerate subpostmasters
OL,4,Cexpected in Parliament 'next month'
OL,6,FAs well as requirements relating to
OL,7,Fpeople eligible for exoneration under
OL,8,Fthe legislation, Mr Hollinrake said
OL,9,Fthose affected would have to sign a
OL,10,Fstatement to the effect that they did
OL,11,Fnot commit the crime for which they
OL,12,Fwere convicted before they could
OL,13,Freceive financial redress.
OL,15,FIf they were subsequently found to
OL,16,Fhave signed the statement falsely, Mr
OL,17,FHollinrake said they "may be guilty of
OL,18,Ffraud".
