OL,4,Cexpected in Parliament 'next month'
OL,6,FIn the Commons, the business minister
OL,7,Fsaid: "We continue to develop our
OL,8,Fresponse to this scandal, and on
OL,9,FThursday I made a written statement
OL,10,Fdetailing the way in which we plan to
OL,11,Flegislate to overturn Horizon-related
OL,12,Fconvictions en masse.
OL,14,F"We expect to introduce that
OL,15,Flegislation as soon as possible next
OL,16,Fmonth."
