OL,4,Cexpected in Parliament 'next month'
OL,6,FElsewhere, Liam Byrne, Labour chairman
OL,7,Fof the business and trade committee,
OL,8,Fsaid there was a "toxic culture of
OL,9,Fdisbelief" of subpostmasters in the
OL,10,FPost Office leadership, adding: "The
OL,11,Fbottom line is that redress is too
OL,12,Fslow and the offers are too low."
OL,14,FMr Hollinrake said he agreed the
OL,15,Fcompensation is "being delivered too
OL,16,Fslowly".
