OL,4,Cexpected in Parliament 'next month'
OL,6,FHe added: "That's something we're
OL,7,Fseeking to accelerate every single
OL,8,Fday, and we're doing good work I think
OL,9,Fwith the advisory board in terms of
OL,10,Ftrying to make sure that's the case.
OL,12,F"I don't think set offers are too low,
OL,13,FI'm not saying there aren't cases
OL,14,Fwhere that is not the case, certainly
OL,15,Fin terms of some of the cases in any
OL,16,Fcompensation scheme will not be 100%
OL,17,Fperfect."
